room_title: Escape room "Illusion" by Timed Out in Charlotte
review: Amber was great game master. We had an awesome time with Illusion. Highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Illusion" by Timed Out in Charlotte
review: We had a great time in Illusion, and Jack was an awesome GameMaster. We will absolutely be back to play the other rooms! Awesome place and awesome people here, highly recommendable!

room_title: Escape room "Illusion" by Timed Out in Charlotte
review: I did the Illusion room. it was my first ever Escape Room. this place provides a fun and professional environment. I got my money's worth and Chris Smiley-face was a great Game Master. I will be returning!

room_title: Escape room "Illusion" by Timed Out in Charlotte
review: Me and 6 other friends did the illusion room! It was so much fun and challenging! Chris was a great game master!!
